   "source": [
    "## 21. The Least Squares Intercept Formula\n",
    "\n",
    "Once the slope is determined, the intercept is:\n",
    "\n",
    "b0 = y_bar - b1 * x_bar\n",
    "\n",
    "This formula guarantees a remarkable geometric property."
   ]
