   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 22. The Regression Line Passes Through the Means\n",
    "\n",
    "The least squares regression line always passes through (x_bar, y_bar), called the point of averages.\n",
    "\n",
    "Proof: Substitute x = x_bar into y_hat = b0 + b1*x.\n",
    "\n",
    "Then y_hat = (y_bar - b1*x_bar) + b1*x_bar = y_bar.\n",
    "\n",
    "Thus (x_bar, y_bar) lies exactly on the regression line."
   ]
